### List all products
GET http://localhost:5155/api/products
Accept: application/json

### Create a product
POST http://localhost:5155/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Laptop",
  "price": 999.99
}

### Validation test — empty name
POST http://localhost:5155/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "",
  "price": 999.99
}

### Validation test — negative price
POST http://localhost:5155/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Laptop",
  "price": -1
}